SELECT sum(courier_price + total_price + unique_code - discount) as total_income FROM `orders` WHERE `order_status` like '%selesai%' and `orders`.`deleted_at` IS NULL LIMIT 1

SELECT `id`, sum(courier_price + total_price + unique_code - discount) as total_income_per_month, (payment_method_id) as payment_method, DATE_FORMAT(updated_at, '%Y-%m') as month_year_income FROM `orders` WHERE `order_status` like '%selesai%' and `orders`.`deleted_at` IS NULL GROUP BY DATE_FORMAT(updated_at, '%Y-%m') ORDER BY `updated_at` ASC
